e-1", "cartservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "frontend-2"], "service_name": ["cartservice", "checkoutservice", "frontend", "redis"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-05", "aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "status_combinations": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,status_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,N/A,frontend-2,hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.,13,HTTP status code: 500,出现次数:564\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,N/A,frontend-1,hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.,13,HTTP status code: 500,出现次数:466\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,N/A,frontend-0,hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.,13,HTTP status code: 500,出现次数:458\n", "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-07T03:10:28Z to 2025-06-07T03:20:28Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-07 03:10:28+00:00 to 2025-06-07 03:20:28+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "根据获得的日志数据，我们可以识别到以下异常调用链和故障模式：\n\n### **检测到的错误关键词**\n- `RedisTimeoutException`\n- `Timeout awaiting response`\n- `FailedPrecondition`\n- `Can't access cart storage`\n\n### **异常模式分析**\n\n#### **流程链1**\n- **Component**: `cartservice`\n- **Reason**: 服务无法访问 Redis 存储，超时等待响应，导致操作无法完成。\n- **Evidence**: 出现于 `cartservice` 调用 Redis 时，例如：\n  ```\n  Error status code 'FailedPrecondition' with detail 'Can't access cart storage. StackExchange.Redis.RedisTimeoutException: Timeout awaiting response (outbound=0KiB, inbound=0KiB, 5669ms elapsed, timeout is 5000ms)\n  ```\n\n#### **流程链2**\n- **Component**: `frontend`\n- **Reason**: 前端调用 `cartservice` 时，因 Redis 操作超时导致请求失败。\n- **Evidence**: 前端多个 pod 会话出现访问购物车无法完成的情况，例如：\n  ```\n  failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = FailedPrecondition desc = Can't access cart storage.\n  ```\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"RedisTimeoutException\", \"Timeout awaiting response\", \"FailedPrecondition\", \"Can't access cart storage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务无法访问 Redis 存储，导致请求超时。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error status code 'FailedPrecondition' with detail 'Can't access cart storage. StackExchange.Redis.RedisTimeoutException: Timeout awaiting response (outbound=0KiB, inbound=0KiB, 5669ms elapsed, timeout is 5000ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"访问购物车时 Redis 操作超时，导致请求失败。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据获取的数据，初步分析如下：\n\n### 发现的异常调用链\n以下是一些显著的异常调用链，定义为延迟倍数大于2.0或遭遇错误状态的调用：\n\n1. **Redis 查询异常**\n   - `cartservice-0 -> redis` 和 `cartservice-1 -> redis`\n     - 操作: `HGET`\n     - 异常延迟大幅增加，从正常的 ~1740ms 增加到 ~5865941ms，倍数 > 2.0，出现时间 20 次。\n     - 同类异常在多个节点上出现，包括 `aiops-k8s-05` 的延迟倍数为 4945。\n\n2. **Cart 服务异常**\n   - 从 `frontend -> cartservice` 的调用，多个操作异常:\n     - `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart`\n     - `POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem`\n     - 延迟从正常的 ~2462ms 增加到 ~5902017ms，倍数 > 2.0。\n\n3. **Checkout 服务异常**\n   - `frontend-2 -> checkoutservice-2`\n     - 操作: `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder`\n     - 延迟从正常的 ~156733ms 增加到 ~5843148ms，倍数 > 2.0。\n     \n### 错误状态\n- 多个 `frontend` 实例（如 `frontend-2`, `frontend-1`）发出 HTTP 500 错误，出现频率高 (564次)，且涉及到接收处理 (`hipstershop.Frontend/Recv.`)。\n\n### 综述\n从分析来看，延迟升高和错误出现集中在 `Cart` 服务链和其关联的 `redis` 操作，以及 `Checkout` 服务上。错误状态则在 `Frontend` 服务上频繁出现。\n\n---\n\n### JSON 格式输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"cartservice-0->redis\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis查询异常延迟从 ~1740ms增加到 ~5865941ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Cart服务调用延迟从 ~2462ms增加到 ~5902017ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkout服务调用延迟从 ~156733ms增加到 ~5843148ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HTTP 500 错误出现次数高达 564 次\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上为初步数据分析结果，接下来可以进行更深入的诊断以确定根因并采取修复措施。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据指标数据分析，从2025-06-07T03:10:28Z到2025-06-07T03:20:28Z期间，系统中存在以下显著异常：\n\n1. **服务级异常**：\n   - `productcatalogservice` 在多个实例（例如：`productcatalogservice-0`，`productcatalogservice-2`）上，`client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 显著增加。\n   - `shippingservice` 也报告了类似的错误增长，尤其是在 `shippingservice-1`。\n   - `frontend` 服务的多个实例（`frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`）存在较高的 `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio`。\n\n2. **请求响应时间异常**：\n   - `redis-cart-0` 上的 `rrt` 和 `rrt_max` 显著增加，暗示数据库可能存在性能问题。\n   - `cartservice` 的多个实例（如 `cartservice-0`, `cartservice-1`, `cartservice-2`）报告了异常高的 `rrt` 和 `rrt_max`。\n   - `checkoutservice-2` 和 `frontend` 服务的实例报告高响应时间。\n\n3. **资源使用异常**：\n   - `productcatalogservice-1` 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 显得不太稳定。\n\n这些异常表明系统在该时段内面临多重服务故障与高负载问题。以下是具体的异常检测结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 显著增加，影响服务可用性。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 0 增加到 60。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio 和 client_error_ratio 高，影响服务稳定性。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从 0 增加到 60。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt 和 rrt_max 异常增加，影响数据库性能。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt 从 213.79 ms 增加至 137271.06 ms。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio 和 server_error_ratio 显著增加，影响用户体验。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio 从 0 增加到 26.68。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 异常增高，导致请求延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max 从 5310.0 增加到 1269305.5。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些异常可能与服务的资源峰值使用或数据库交互性能问题有关，建议对相应组件进行进一步的日志分析和性能调优。"}
